<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thangvan sang leh khawvel cheng a hin,
 A hawih pen na min ka hukdampa;
 Ei nemding umlo sakmin haw cheng lak ah,
 Nang lo chu ka Lal leh hukdampa.

[V2]
 Aw Isu na min a hawih diek hi,
 La sa'n chawian ka ka thih geiin;
 Kei dinga Lul pen na Chanchin pha hi,
 Ka thamuonna pen leh kipahna.

[V3]
 2. Aw Isu ka Lal leh hukdampa,
 A mak na e nei hehpihna chu;
 Bang ziekin ahim kei migilo pen di'n,
 Na hung thih tak le Van lal Chapa ?

[V4]
 3. Lalpa Isu na Chanchin pha hii
 Ka lunggil ah hung cheng zing ta hen;
 Nicheng ka hinna nang din pak gimlim in,
 Hungsuok ta hen tin ka hun pie tai.</lyrics>
<title>Thangvan Sang leh Khawvel</title>
<hymn_number>318</hymn_number>
</song>